{"title":"Docker安装Nginx","uid":"8921f219ac1cdcf63bd94ba3e8d2edd1","slug":"Docker安装Nginx","date":"2022-02-11T09:22:11.000Z","updated":"2022-03-28T02:58:33.287Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Docker安装Nginx.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://imgapi.cn/api.php?zd=zsy&fl=fengjing&gs=images","content":"<h1 id=\"Docker安装Niginx\"><a href=\"#Docker安装Niginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Docker安装Niginx\"></a>Docker安装Niginx</h1><h2 id=\"搜索镜像\"><a href=\"#搜索镜像\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搜索镜像\"></a>搜索镜像</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">docker serach nginx</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://image-1308272335.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image/1638189703600.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"拉取镜像\"><a href=\"#拉取镜像\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"拉取镜像\"></a>拉取镜像</h2><p>拉取最新镜像</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">docker pull nginx:latest</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"查看镜像\"><a href=\"#查看镜像\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看镜像\"></a>查看镜像</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">docker image ls</code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://image-1308272335.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image/1638189857612.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"运行nginx\"><a href=\"#运行nginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行nginx\"></a>运行nginx</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">docker run nginx -d -p 80:80 nginx</code></pre>\n<p><strong>这时候我们已经可以访问到 nginx 的首页了</strong><br><strong>但是如果我们需要配置nginx则比较麻烦 需要：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">docker exec -it nginx bash</code></pre>\n<p>在镜像里面配置</p>\n<h2 id=\"挂载宿主机配置\"><a href=\"#挂载宿主机配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"挂载宿主机配置\"></a>挂载宿主机配置</h2><p>删除刚才启动的nginx镜像<br>重新启动并挂载宿主机目录</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">docker run --name nginx -d \\\n\t--restart&#x3D;always \\\n\t--privileged&#x3D;true \\\n\t-v &#x2F;data&#x2F;env&#x2F;docker&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;html:&#x2F;usr&#x2F;share&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;html \\\n\t-v &#x2F;data&#x2F;env&#x2F;docker&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf&#x2F;nginx.conf:&#x2F;etc&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;nginx.conf \\\n\t-v &#x2F;data&#x2F;env&#x2F;docker&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf&#x2F;conf.d&#x2F;default.conf:&#x2F;etc&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf.d&#x2F;default.conf \\\n\t-v &#x2F;data&#x2F;env&#x2F;docker&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;log:&#x2F;var&#x2F;log&#x2F;nginx \\\n\t-v &#x2F;data&#x2F;env&#x2F;docker&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;ssl:&#x2F;ssl&#x2F; \\\n\t-p 443:443 -p 80:80 \\\nnginx</code></pre>\n<p><strong>这样在我们的宿主机修改配置即可！</strong></p>\n","text":"Docker安装Niginx搜索镜像docker serach nginx 拉取镜像拉取最新镜像 docker pull nginx:latest 查看镜像docker image ls 运行nginxdocker run nginx -d -p 80:80 nginx 这时候我...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":898,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Docker","slug":"Docker","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Docker.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Docker","slug":"Docker","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Docker.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Docker%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Niginx\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Docker安装Niginx</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">搜索镜像</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%96%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">拉取镜像</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">查看镜像</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8Cnginx\"><span class=\"toc-text\">运行nginx</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%AE%BF%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">挂载宿主机配置</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"zniceya","slug":"zni